# CODEOWNERS
# ============================================================================
# Code Ownership Configuration for SARAISE
# Reference: docs/architecture/engineering-governance-and-pr-controls.md § 3
# ============================================================================
#
# This file defines code ownership for automatic review assignment.
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# GOVERNANCE RULES (engineering-governance-and-pr-controls.md § 3):
# - Each repository MUST have Primary and Secondary owners
# - Tier 0 (Critical) owners must be senior engineers approved by leadership
# - Owners are responsible for reviewing architectural compliance
# - Owners can block unsafe changes and escalate violations

# ============================================================================
# TIER 0 — Critical (Highest Control)
# Direct impact on security, isolation, or correctness
# Changes can affect all tenants
# Minimum 2 senior reviewers required
# ============================================================================

# Authentication & Session Management (FROZEN ARCHITECTURE)
/backend/src/core/session_manager.py          @saraise/security-team @saraise/platform-owners
/backend/src/core/auth*.py                    @saraise/security-team @saraise/platform-owners
/backend/src/modules/auth/                    @saraise/security-team @saraise/platform-owners

# Policy Engine (FROZEN ARCHITECTURE)
/backend/src/core/policy_engine*.py           @saraise/security-team @saraise/platform-owners

# Control Plane
/backend/src/core/control_plane/              @saraise/platform-owners

# Runtime Plane
/backend/src/core/runtime/                    @saraise/platform-owners

# Core Security
/backend/src/core/sod_rules.py                @saraise/security-team @saraise/platform-owners
/backend/src/core/role_hierarchy.py           @saraise/security-team @saraise/platform-owners

# ============================================================================
# TIER 1 — Platform Supporting
# Observability, Infrastructure, CI/CD
# ============================================================================

# Infrastructure & DevOps
/.github/                                      @saraise/platform-ops @saraise/platform-owners
/docker-compose*.yml                          @saraise/platform-ops
/Dockerfile*                                  @saraise/platform-ops
/scripts/                                     @saraise/platform-ops

# CI/CD Configuration
/.github/workflows/                           @saraise/platform-ops @saraise/platform-owners

# Observability
/backend/src/core/logging*.py                 @saraise/platform-ops
/backend/src/core/metrics*.py                 @saraise/platform-ops

# ============================================================================
# TIER 2 — Application & Modules
# ERP modules, industry packages, UI applications
# ============================================================================

# Backend Modules
/backend/src/modules/                         @saraise/backend-team

# Frontend Application
/frontend/src/                                @saraise/frontend-team

# ============================================================================
# DOCUMENTATION & ARCHITECTURE
# Architecture docs require platform owner review
# ============================================================================

# Architecture Documentation (FROZEN DOMAINS)
